N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 ยง 263.1 - Scope

State Regulations

The rules in Part 263 apply to all proceedings brought
under the Farm Laborers' Fair Labor Practices Act ("FLFLPA"). These rules shall
be liberally construed and shall not be deemed to limit the powers conferred on
the board by SERA. Notes
